Nürnberg, 1945. In den Ruinen einer vom Krieg gezeichneten Stadt erhält der US-amerikanische Psychiater Dr. Douglas M. Kelley den Auftrag, die inhaftierten Hauptverantwortlichen des NS-Regimes in Vorbereitung auf die Nürnberger Prozesse zu untersuchen. Unter ihnen ist auch der ehemalige Reichsmarschall Hermann Göring, dessen Intelligenz, Charisma und Gerissenheit Kelley zugleich herausfordern und faszinieren. Trotz anfänglicher Machtspiele gelingt es dem Arzt, Görings Vertrauen zu gewinnen und Einblick in seine Persönlichkeit zu erhalten. Während im Gerichtssaal die Verhandlungen beginnen, fällt es Kelley jedoch zunehmend schwerer, die notwendige Distanz zu seinem Klienten zu wahren.

snippet.title: Lorna Shore - In Darkness (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Lorna Shore - In Darkness - Official Video. On Tour Now in Europe/UK + North American Tour this spring!

From the new album 'I Feel The Everblack Festering Within Me' - Out Now. Get it now: 
https://ifeeltheeverblackfesteringwithinme.com/
https://lornashoreband.com/

'In Darkness' is about growing up feeling distant from everyone- a song about anxiety and being an outcast (as many of us metal fans grow from). It’s a song about embracing that outlandish and ostracized feeling. Knowing that we have grown in the shadows, the darkness- of the world, but accepting that through that darkness we have become. - WILL RAMOS

LYRICS //

WE ARE ALIVE
I WATCH THE SHADOWS
FALL ON HORIZONS WE ECHO
WE ARE THE DIFFERENCE
A CONGREGATION OF LIKE MINDED HUES AND SEPARATION
AN INTROVERSION OF LIFE
AM I BROKEN, LOST, BATTERED AND TOSSED
I WAS THE ONE ON THE OUTSIDE SEARCHING FOR PEACE I WOULD NEVER FIND
BLACK ROSES LOOM IN THE DARK
NEVER TO FALL APART
WE WERE PERFECTLY SEWN OVER IMPERFECT BONES
WE MADE A HOME IN THE SHADOW OF MADNESS

WE LIVE IN DARKNESS
WE COME TO LIFE
IN DARKNESS WE WON’T DIE
WE WILL SURVIVE
BENEATH THE VALLEYS OF DARKNESS
BETWEEN MOUNTAINS OF DELIVERANCE
WE FOUND A HOME BURIED BELOW
THE SHADOWS IN BETWEEN THE RABBLE WE LET GO
WE’RE NOT MISPLACED, NAUGHT, CURSÈD AND ROT
WE ARE THE ONES BURNING INSIDE
THIS IS HOW IT FEELS TO BE ALIVE
MOONFLOWERS BLOOM IN THE DARK
NEVER TO FALL APART

WE LIVE IN DARKNESS
IN DARKNESS RAVE
EXALT THE FIGHT
IN THIS EMPTINESS WE COME TO LIFE
IN DARKNESS WE ARE ALIVE
WE WERE PERFECTLY SEWN OVER IMPERFECT BONES
WE MADE A HOME IN THE SHADOW OF MADNESS

WE LIVE IN DARKNESS
IN DARKNESS RAVE
EXALT THE FIGHT
IN THIS EMPTINESS WE COME TO LIFE
IN DARKNESS WE ARE ALIVE
WE WILL SURVIVE
IN DARKNESS WE ARE ALIVE

////

snippet.title: Trailer-REACTION | DIE ODYSSEE, Monarch - Legacy of Monsters, Glennkill - Ein Schafskrimi
snippet.description:
Schafe, Staubsauger und Sirenen: wir schauen den ersten Teaser zu DIE ODYSSEE. Hatten wir bislang noch keine Zeit zu. Daneben blicken Andre und Antje aber auch noch auf den viel versprechenden Trailer zu GLENNKILL: EIN SCHAFSKRIMI, die ersten Schnipsel zu HOKUM und noch mehr Mysteriöses in Form von UNDERTONE. Abgerundet durch Sympathisches wie die vielschichtige Geistergeschichte namens A USEFUL GHOST und den Beats pumpenden Kuhhirten namens DJ AHMET bevor es noch mal mit LEE CRONIN'S THE MUMMY sowohl klassisch wie gruselig, als auch neu interpretiert wird. Sagt uns doch gern, welche Vorschau Euch davon am meisten überzeugt hat und bleibt ansonsten bitte so gesund wie gut drauf. Wir sehen uns. Adios.

snippet.title: Apashe & Alina Pash - Kyiv
snippet.description:
This project was filmed in Ukraine during the war. The choir was recorded on a calm day, between nights of air raids and shelling. As I’m writing this, Kyiv is in a blackout.

This city has always meant a great deal to me, and I hope this video can, in one way or another, help people understand what is happening there.

The artist proceeds will be donated to charity. If you'd like to support it further, you'll find a link below.

Charity Link: http://patron8.childrenheroes.org/

Hymns of Resilience EP: https://bit.ly/hymns-of-resilience

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revival’s 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tom Fogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order of the day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.    

During their short time together as a band (1968 – 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. They’ve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revival’s canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like “Bad Moon Rising,” “Down on the Corner,” “Fortunate Son,” “Have You Ever Seen the Rain,” “Proud Mary,” “Born on the Bayou,” “Travelin’ Band” and “Up Around the Bend” have been ingrained into pop culture — not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, America’s greatest rock ’n’ roll band.

#ccr #creedenceclearwaterrevival #fortunateson
